WEBVTT

00:04.369 --> 00:06.236
       (ENGINE STARTING)        

00:07.371 --> 00:09.872
      Oh, I'm so nervous.       

00:09.874 --> 00:12.975
     -Don't sweat it, Daph.     
     You'll do great.           
     -SCOOBY-DOO: Mmm-mmm.      

00:12.977 --> 00:14.609
         You think so?          

00:14.611 --> 00:17.244
  Yeah, driving tests are easy. 
  Even I passed mine.           

00:19.113 --> 00:21.647
         Yeah, me too!          

00:21.649 --> 00:24.850
 Daphne, you're gonna be great. 
 I believe in you.              

00:24.852 --> 00:27.285
          -We all do!           
          -ALL: Yeah.           

00:27.287 --> 00:30.655
  If you put your mind to it,   
  you can do anything, Daphne.  

00:30.657 --> 00:32.990
      ALL: Yeah! Right on!      

00:32.992 --> 00:35.892
     -You've got what it takes. 
     Right, guys?               
     -ALL: Yeah.                

00:35.894 --> 00:37.493
          -Yeah?                
          -ALL: Yeah!           

00:37.495 --> 00:38.727
          -Yeah?                
          -ALL: Yeah!           

00:38.729 --> 00:40.295
           All right!           

00:40.297 --> 00:41.629
       (TIRES SCREECHING)       

00:41.631 --> 00:42.896
          -Oh...                
          -(CRASHING)           

00:44.565 --> 00:46.132
         VELMA: Oh, no.         

00:46.134 --> 00:47.566
         (MAN GROANING)         

00:48.868 --> 00:51.135
        So, did I pass?         

